{
  "stem": "19921.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Let me see-- one, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] two couple-- that's three.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that one couple had five children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then another couple-- yeah, another couple with two-- with three children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So many couples were living in that particular house-- each one in a room.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, that one couple which was only a man and a wife, there was no room for them, so they had to sleep in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On the floor, because--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They all were taken from the same place in Lwow-- not from the same building.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We all met, except for myself, my uncle, and my brother-in-law-- as-- as later developed, he became my brother-in-law, because I married my-- my sister-in-law's sister, so we became brother-in-law.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But at that particular time, we were strangers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They all came from different area in Lwow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't know each other, except for that-- the six-- I mean, those four people which we knew.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The rest were all strangers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was it there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And our job-- a day later, we got assignments.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They put us together on a-- you know, with-- that they didn't call everybody in, just, you know, house by house.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they tell us what our assignments will be.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the first warning was, forget about-- they were asking us from what town we are.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And just forget about this town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "From now on, this town, you're going to build right here in this area.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Forget about a home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That's your home.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they assigned us to take the trees down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The forest-- not trees.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Giant trees, giant forest.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "No-- there was not a-- people who didn't-- had a foot in this thing, in that forest, when they brought us to that section there.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
